Description: The BioSamples database aggregates sample information for reference samples (e.g. Coriell Cell lines) and samples for which data exist in one of the EBI's assay databases such as ArrayExpress- the European Nucleotide Archive or PRoteomics Identificates DatabasE. It provides links to assays an specific samples- and accepts direct submissions of sample information.
